column5: Just got back from a quick plane trip,(had to make sure nothing was siezed) and I can report alls well.        That should catch his attention.

Wayne??????????????  Would that be THE Wayne with 8,263 posts????  Never heard of him,   :lol:  :lol:  Must be a newbie.  Either that, or he is on holidays up in Temagami, with a soon side trip to Lakair.
Yeah...I keep wondering when Wayne Newton will perform again...I know he's old, but hey...those are classics.
LOL...I didn't say he was good looking...just that his songs are classics....LOL  His voice is a bit odd though isn't it??? haha.
Yeah, 50 year olds with lisps are scary.
Yes, Wayne please come back. The thread counts are way down, laddie!

Its really strange to see that Wayne is not the top poster of the day  This vacation will give him plenty of time to accumalate some fish pics for a decent report  Which he was lacking.  What I do miss is how willing Wayne is to go out of his way to help others.  MTP
